            <title><![CDATA[HR Platform: Project Launch]]></title>
            <link>https://localhostlegends.github.io/documentation/blog/2026/03/20/project-launch</link>
            <guid>https://localhostlegends.github.io/documentation/blog/2026/03/20/project-launch</guid>
            <pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[We're thrilled to announce the official launch of the HR Platform development project! 🎉]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>We're thrilled to announce the official launch of the <strong>HR Platform</strong> development project! 🎉</p>
<p>Today marks the beginning of our journey to build a modern HR Tech solution for workforce management.</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="what-is-hr-platform">What is HR Platform?<a href="https://localhostlegends.github.io/documentation/blog/2026/03/20/project-launch#what-is-hr-platform" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to What is HR Platform?" title="Direct link to What is HR Platform?" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>HR Platform is a comprehensive web portal designed to automate and streamline HR processes for medium and large companies. Our goal is to create a solution that bridges the gap between HR departments and employees, making workforce management efficient and transparent.</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="project-scope">Project Scope<a href="https://localhostlegends.github.io/documentation/blog/2026/03/20/project-launch#project-scope" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Project Scope" title="Direct link to Project Scope" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>The platform will include:</p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="core-modules">Core Modules<a href="https://localhostlegends.github.io/documentation/blog/2026/03/20/project-launch#core-modules" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Core Modules" title="Direct link to Core Modules" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<ul>
<li class=""><strong>👥 Employee Management</strong> - Complete employee lifecycle management</li>
<li class=""><strong>📝 Recruitment</strong> - Streamlined hiring process</li>
<li class=""><strong>📊 Analytics</strong> - Real-time dashboards and reports</li>
<li class=""><strong>🔐 Authentication</strong> - Secure role-based access control</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="technical-stack">Technical Stack<a href="https://localhostlegends.github.io/documentation/blog/2026/03/20/project-launch#technical-stack" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Technical Stack" title="Direct link to Technical Stack" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<ul>
<li class=""><strong>Backend</strong>: NestJS with TypeScript</li>
<li class=""><strong>Database</strong>: PostgreSQL with TypeORM</li>
<li class=""><strong>Authentication</strong>: JWT + Argon2</li>
<li class=""><strong>Documentation</strong>: Docusaurus</li>
<li class=""><strong>Deployment</strong>: Docker + GitHub Actions</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="development-timeline">Development Timeline<a href="https://localhostlegends.github.io/documentation/blog/2026/03/20/project-launch#development-timeline" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Development Timeline" title="Direct link to Development Timeline" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="phase-1-march---april-2026">Phase 1 (March - April 2026)<a href="https://localhostlegends.github.io/documentation/blog/2026/03/20/project-launch#phase-1-march---april-2026" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Phase 1 (March - April 2026)" title="Direct link to Phase 1 (March - April 2026)" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<ul>
<li class="">✅ Project setup and architecture</li>
<li class="">✅ User authentication module</li>
<li class="">✅ Employee CRUD operations</li>
<li class="">✅ API documentation</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="phase-2-may---june-2026">Phase 2 (May - June 2026)<a href="https://localhostlegends.github.io/documentation/blog/2026/03/20/project-launch#phase-2-may---june-2026" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Phase 2 (May - June 2026)" title="Direct link to Phase 2 (May - June 2026)" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<ul>
<li class="">Recruitment module</li>
<li class="">Advanced search and filters</li>
<li class="">Email notifications</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="phase-3-july---august-2026">Phase 3 (July - August 2026)<a href="https://localhostlegends.github.io/documentation/blog/2026/03/20/project-launch#phase-3-july---august-2026" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Phase 3 (July - August 2026)" title="Direct link to Phase 3 (July - August 2026)" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<ul>
<li class="">Analytics dashboard</li>
<li class="">Reporting system</li>
<li class="">Performance reviews</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="get-involved">Get Involved<a href="https://localhostlegends.github.io/documentation/blog/2026/03/20/project-launch#get-involved" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Get Involved" title="Direct link to Get Involved" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>We're building in the open! Follow our progress:</p>
<ul>
<li class=""><strong>GitHub</strong>: <a href="https://github.com/LocalhostLegends/backend" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="">LocalhostLegends/backend</a></li>
<li class=""><strong>Documentation</strong>: <a class="" href="https://localhostlegends.github.io/documentation/docs/intro">Check our docs</a></li>
<li class=""><strong>Issues</strong>: Report bugs or request features</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="stay-connected">Stay Connected<a href="https://localhostlegends.github.io/documentation/blog/2026/03/20/project-launch#stay-connected" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Stay Connected" title="Direct link to Stay Connected" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>This blog will be updated regularly with:</p>
<ul>
<li class="">Development updates</li>
<li class="">New feature announcements</li>
<li class="">Technical deep dives</li>
<li class="">Release notes</li>
</ul>
<p>Let's build something great together! 🚀</p>
<p><em>— HR Platform Team</em></p>]]></content:encoded>
